OL,6,FTwo teenagers attacked a man while he
OL,7,Ffor a taxi in in an unprovoked attack,
OL,8,Fa court has heard.
OL,10,FJoshua Jones, now 21, and Thomas
OL,11,FMcArthur-King, now 20, repeatedly
OL,12,Fpunched and kicked the victim, before
OL,13,Fknocking him to the ground and
OL,14,Fcontinuing to kick him.
OL,16,FAfter the assault, heard how a
OL,17,Fshirtless McArthur-King took out his
OL,18,Fphone to take a picture of the victim.
