OL,6,FThe injured man says the attack has
OL,7,Fleft him with a badly damaged knee and
OL,8,Fpost-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD).
OL,10,FProsecutor Dean Pulling said the
OL,11,Fassault happened in the early hours of
OL,12,F1 May, 2022, in Carmarthen town
OL,13,Fcentre, in the grounds of Christ
OL,14,FChurch.
OL,16,FThe court heard the victim and his
OL,17,Ffriend were waiting to meet a pre-
OL,18,Fbooked taxi after a night out, when
OL,19,FMcArthur-King delivered a "flying
OL,20,Fkick" to the complainant's friend.
