OL,6,FThen he and Jones turned their
OL,7,Fattention to the victim, repeatedly
OL,8,Fpunching and kicking him. When he fell
OL,9,Fto the floor, the attack continued
OL,10,Fwith the pair kicking the victim.
OL,12,FThe prosecutor read a statement from
OL,13,Fthe victim in which he described the
OL,14,Fimpact of the incident.
