OL,6,FHe said he no longer goes out
OL,7,Fsocialising with friends and was
OL,8,Fsuffering with post-traumatic stress
OL,9,Fdisorder and panic attacks. He said
OL,10,Fthe assault changed the way he now
OL,11,Flives his life, adding: "Quite
OL,12,Ffrankly, it ruined my life."
OL,14,FLawyers defending Jones and McArthur-
OL,15,FKing both told the court the violence
OL,16,Foutside the church was "out of
OL,17,Fcharacter" for their clients.
