OL,6,FRepresenting Jones, Hannah George said
OL,7,Fas a teenager her client had acted as
OL,8,Fa carer for his mother until she
OL,9,Fpassed away. Following her death, she
OL,10,Fdescribed how he "lost himself" in
OL,11,Falcohol and tried to drown out his
OL,12,Femotions.
OL,14,FMcArthur-King's legal representative,
OL,15,FCaitlin Brazel said her client had a
OL,16,F"troubled upbringing", having lost his
OL,17,Ffather at the age of nine and then
OL,18,Fexperiencing two "extremely abusive
OL,19,Fstep-fathers".
