OL,6,FHanding down his judgement, Judge Paul
OL,7,FThomas KC told the pair that,
OL,8,Ffollowing the attack, they had
OL,9,Freceived "two undeserved matters of
OL,10,Ffortune"; namely the decision to
OL,11,Fcharge them with unlawful wounding
OL,12,Frather than the more serious charge of
OL,13,Fgrievous bodily harm.
OL,15,FWith discounts for their guilty pleas,
OL,16,Fthe defendants were each sentenced to
OL,17,F20 months in prison suspended for 18
OL,18,Fmonths. They were also ordered to
OL,19,Fcomplete a rehabilitation course and
OL,20,Fto do 200 hours of unpaid work.
